Original work
-------------
Protocol SIFT was created by Rob Lee and the teamdfir project
(https://github.com/teamdfir/protocol-sift). The DFIR Orchestrator
configuration, the SANS SIFT skill files, the per-case templates, and the
report tooling derive from that original work.

Modifications and additions
---------------------------
The NTP / time-sync enrichment feature and supporting material in this
repository were contributed by ciphentech for the SANS FindEvil Hackathon,
including:

  - skills/ntp-enrichment/SKILL.md
  - analysis-scripts/ntp_resolver.py, ntp_nist_client.py, ntp_enricher.py,
    ntp_manifest.py, sift_logger.py
  - the global logging / observability hooks under global/hooks/
  - the associated tests and documentation

